title: Farenzeit 451 8/26: Kenosha, Laura, Britney Spears, National Dog Day, NBA
itunes:title: Farenzeit 451 8/26: Kenosha, Laura, Britney Spears, National Dog Day, NBA
description:
On this edition of Farenzeit 451 Jack and Miles discuss the murder of 2 protesters in Kenosha, WI last night and the apprehension of the killer, Hurricane Laura is getting stronger as it approaches Texas and Louisiana, Britney is expressing dissatisfaction with her conservatorship, it's National Dog Day, and the Milwaukee Bucks are not coming out to play Game 5 of the Playoffs to protest police violence in Kenosha.
